@using Conversey.UI_MVC.Resources
@model Conversey.UI_MVC.Models.AiAdmin.AiModelsViewModel
@inject IAdminI18nService I18n
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = I18n["Configure Models"] + ": " + Model.Provider.ProviderName;
    var availableModels = Model.AvailableModels;
    var fetchError = Model.FetchError;
    var hasModels = availableModels.Count > 0;
}

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 px-4 py-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">@I18n["Configure Models"]: @Model.Provider.ProviderName</h1>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">@I18n["Select which models to use for AI operations."]</p>
            </div>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Providers")" class="text-sm text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">&larr; @I18n["Back to Providers"]</a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
                <div class="border-b border-gray-200 px-6 py-4">
                    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">@I18n["Provider Connection"]</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="px-6 py-4">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-gray-500">@I18n["Base URL"]</h3>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-mono text-gray-700">@(string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(Model.Provider.BaseUrl) ? "—" : Model.Provider.BaseUrl)</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-gray-500">@I18n["API Key"]</h3>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-mono text-gray-700">@(string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(Model.Provider.ApiKey) ? "—" : new string('*', Math.Min(Model.Provider.ApiKey.Length, 20)))</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3">
                        <a href="@Url.Action("EditProvider", new { id = Model.Provider.Id })" class="text-sm text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700">@I18n["Edit connection settings"]</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(fetchError))
            {
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4 shadow-sm">
                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-amber-800">@I18n["Could not fetch models from provider API."]</p>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-amber-600">@fetchError</p>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-amber-600">@I18n["You can still enter model names manually below."]</p>
                </div>
            }

            @if (hasModels)
            {
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-green-200 bg-green-50 p-4 shadow-sm">
                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800">@availableModels.Count @I18n["model(s) found."]</p>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-green-600">@I18n["Select from the dropdowns below, or type a model name manually."]</p>
                </div>
            }

            <form asp-action="SaveModels" asp-route-id="@Model.Provider.Id" method="post" class="space-y-6">
                @Html.AntiForgeryToken()

                <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
                    <div class="border-b border-gray-200 px-6 py-4">
                        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">@I18n["Model Selection"]</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="px-6 py-4 space-y-4">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-gray-500">@I18n["Completions Model"]</label>
                            <div class="mt-1 flex gap-2">
                                @if (hasModels)
                                {
                                    <select name="CompletionsModel" class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 font-mono text-sm text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                                        <option value="">— @I18n["select or type manually"] —</option>
                                        @foreach (var m in availableModels)
                                        {
                                            var selected = string.Equals(m, Model.Provider.CompletionsModel, StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase);
                                            <option value="@m" selected="@selected">@m</option>
                                        }
                                    </select>
                                }
                                <input name="CompletionsModel" type="text" class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 font-mono text-sm text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-indigo-500 @(hasModels ? "hidden" : "")" placeholder="mistral-small-latest" list="completions-datalist" />
                                @if (hasModels)
                                {
                                    <datalist id="completions-datalist">
                                        @foreach (var m in availableModels)
                                        {
                                            <option value="@m" />
                                        }
                                    </datalist>
                                }
                            </div>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">@I18n["Used for: idea nudging, ranking, categorization, alternative generation."]</p>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-gray-500">@I18n["Moderation Model"]</label>
                            <div class="mt-1 flex gap-2">
                                @if (hasModels)
                                {
                                    <select name="ModerationModel" class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 font-mono text-sm text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                                        <option value="">— @I18n["none (skip moderation)"] —</option>
                                        @foreach (var m in availableModels)
                                        {
                                            var selected = string.Equals(m, Model.Provider.ModerationModel, StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase);
                                            <option value="@m" selected="@selected">@m</option>
                                        }
                                    </select>
                                }
                                <input name="ModerationModel" type="text" class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 font-mono text-sm text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-indigo-500 @(hasModels ? "hidden" : "")" placeholder="mistral-moderation-latest" list="moderation-datalist" />
                                @if (hasModels)
                                {
                                    <datalist id="moderation-datalist">
                                        @foreach (var m in availableModels)
                                        {
                                            <option value="@m" />
                                        }
                                    </datalist>
                                }
                            </div>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">@I18n["Used for content moderation. Leave empty for prompt-based fallback."]</p>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-gray-500">@I18n["Temperature"]</label>
                            <input name="Temperature" type="number" min="0" max="2" step="0.1" value="@Model.Provider.Temperature" class="mt-1 w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-indigo-500" placeholder="1.0" />
                            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">@I18n["Controls randomness: 0 = deterministic, 2 = creative."]</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-3">
                    <a href="@Url.Action("Providers")" class="rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50">
                        @I18n["Skip (save later)"]
                    </a>
                    <button type="submit" class="rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-700">
                        @I18n["Save Models"]
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
